                "unit_combination": "(%)"
              },
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "LINAC"
                ],
                "institute": "1USALAS"
              },
              "free_text": [
                "Irradiations at 200 MeV were performed",
                "at Alamos Neutron Science Center(LANSCE) facility",
                "using the dual-energy capability of the 800 MeV",
                "side-coupled cavity linac. Irradiations at 100 MeV",
                "were performed at the LANSCE Isotope Production",
                "Facility, using proton beam from a drift tube linac"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Natural Th target was used. A target stack comprised",
                "six foil packets,each packet containing two thorium",
                "foils and one aluminum monitor foil. Natural thorium",
                "foils were of 99.7% purity.The foils had the",
                "dimensions of approximately 2.5cm x 2.5 cm and had",
                "thicknesses ranging from 60.5 to 70.5 mg/cm2.",
                "A similar sized aluminum beam current monitoring foil",
                "of 99.9% purity with a thickness of approximately",
                "65 mg/cm2 was incorporated downstream of each set of",
                "thorium foils. All foils were sandwiched between",
                "single layers of 25 mu-m thick Kapton tape, which",
                "served as a catcher foil for recoil ions."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI",
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "The thorium foils were counted on an ORTEC",
                "GEM10P4-70 detector with a relative efficiency of 10%,",
                "while the aluminum foils were counted on a Princeton",
                "Gamma-tech lithium-drifted germanium Ge(Li)detector",
                "with a relative efficiency of 13.7%."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Cross sections were determined from analysis",
                "of gamma ray decay curves, followed over period of",
                "several months."
              ]
            }
          ],
